title: Fading Fournette, Backing Back-Ups, and More Daily Decisions | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck break down the daily fantasy players to go big on, save your money on, and buy low on. Plus, their contrarian plays, bargain-bin picks, and their daily fantasy lineup for Week 6.
